  "abstract": "With the increasing complexity of interventional radiology (IR) procedures and the growing availability of electronic health records, simplifying IR reports is critical to improving patient understanding and clinical decision-making. This study provides insights into the performance of various LLMs in rewriting IR reports, which can help in selecting the most suitable model for clinical patient-centered applications.",
